---
title: One Pot Chicken and Red Lentil Dal with Spinach and Naans
description: Packed with delicious, good-for-you ingredients, our warming chicken and red lentil dal is the perfect recipe for cosy nights at home. Bright, delicious, and a rich source of protein, red lentils are a great ingredient to bulk out stews, sauces and curries. Served with soft naan bread to keep you feeling full, this wholesome dish is a guaranteed crowd-pleaser.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pot-chicken-and-red-lentil-dal-130b419c-c5857c27.jpg
